{"tid":1286682,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"堅決反對為武漢發聲","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:55.000Z","uid":264780,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94aafb1fbe006d6c7e0918e0f49386a9a0f364d8","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"堅決<span style=\"color: red;\">反對為武漢發聲</span>嘅巴絲<br />\n如果喺台灣，係咪會用同一個道理<br />\n去反對<span style=\"color: red;\">為香港發聲</span><br />\n去反對<span style=\"color: red;\">台港連線</span><br />\n去反對<span style=\"color: red;\">反紅媒</span><br />\n<br />\n因為香港係中國嘅事<br />\n鄰國既事關我地撚事<br />\n要幫香港既反香港住啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為台灣都未搞掂，唔好理香港<br />\n自己都未顧掂仲要顧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係好無情 但係我地幫唔到香港<br />\nOn99幫佢爭取埋民主好冇<br />\n要搞香港聲援唔該自己喺第二度搞<br />\n開多條戰線唔化算<br />\n做好自己，唔洗理人<br />\n你自己台灣都未撚搞得掂憑咩去救香港<br />\n<br />\n支持香港既去香港支持, 支持台灣既留係台灣<br />\n<br />\n你撈埋香港一齊訴求只會把台灣自貶為中国一個城市，令我地嘅抗爭變成中国城市嘅市政事務。<br />\n<br />\n別人國家內不要干預<br />\n<br />\n我們還有很多台灣人的事要幫手<br />\n<br />\n香港事香港了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣要幫香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dacbea5f3c92f7e844be60f6206c8cda8cea71","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"從香港反送中一事，睇得出 PTT 已被滲透<br />\n<br />\n不斷帶風向令運動失焦<br />\n我唔理係真心中華膠定五毛"},{"pid":"84dc76111a7e1ffd73e17674a82b64ddca51e066","tid":1286682,"uid":251292,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"班蝗永遠都唔會係我地既同路人"},{"pid":"05cd29dd428042b21461d43db97632fa09cc0cc6","tid":1286682,"uid":229460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30af641b1c3537dec7c289994c8581d455041e0c","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"成班中二病聲援香港 救世主呀當自己？"},{"pid":"a158ba15f93d7d80389f1371694223020d402639","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"笑撚死仲一班 PTT 仔話聲援班香港支畜"},{"pid":"26a40768ac29af9ec0277548db1cc6ef90c089c7","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"邊個話要支援香港 呢條友一撚定係鬼<br />\n<br />\n唔好比人引導焦點<br />\n記住香港既事我地冇能力去理<br />\n亦都係唔到我地去理"},{"pid":"fab01e9eccab50870bc8ed9a96c7c647a9a7b693","tid":1286682,"uid":263584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgZoV8O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgZoV8O.gif&h=e09e1b5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34903bedba8f4c694d1844990f1a094f32283d4","tid":1286682,"uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"仲嘈緊武漢一事既巴打 記住只係 &quot;聲&quot; 援<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/deBGAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/deBGAS</a><br />\n<br />\n請睇睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兄弟不必嘈交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />77照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f91e70102f218ffdeb65e74c24353efd3c9034b","tid":1286682,"uid":55955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:19.000Z","msg":"台灣係支持香港爭取民主，兩邊理念一致<br />\n焚化爐關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f00b32c48355f63bc0642403e2cc773252c56","tid":1286682,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f91e70102f218ffdeb65e74c24353efd3c9034b","tid":1286682,"uid":55955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:19.000Z","msg":"台灣係支持香港爭取民主，兩邊理念一致<br />\n焚化爐關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"至少呢個理由好好多，好過第一個 post 嘅理由"},{"pid":"9692d4c6b617271f7478c918b0a7534129495fe1","tid":1286682,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山各自努力係講緊爬緊同一座山<br />\n即係有相同目的（反送中以及相關訴求）但唔會因為其手段（勇武/和理非）而割席<br />\n<br />\n武漢已經係第二座山。唔係爬同一座山點解要支持？<br />\n<br />\n再講點解唔叫武漢人支持返香港反送中訴求？"},{"pid":"2f255c7503b017cea411a7c6a396c68fb6d3e700","tid":1286682,"uid":252854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiOkYZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiOkYZA.jpg&h=881b89e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇Twitter啲片佢哋示威舉嘅橫額係「習大大救救我」仲會跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9KPSjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9KPSjH.jpg&h=641b5705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下面啲大陸人留言，佢哋最清楚自己人嘅奴性，所以話大陸同香港係真係有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點都好麻煩唔好同77遊行五大訴求搞埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYceiZ0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYceiZ0.gif&h=73c39156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c896ca0c24a8ec553a1